<br>
The macro button is available right after failure.<br>
<br>
My suggestion would be to try not judge the level of the mob you are attempting to cast upon simply by the color con.  A light blue to someone who is level 65, can and will mean that it could be over level 46.  Better to know the mob level for certain, than go by the color.  Just my 2 cents. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center><img border=0 src="http://www.speakeasy.org/~robtony/CattSignature.gif"></center><BR>
